title: Curley Williams - Half As Much - Bear Family CD (2005)
description:
Curley Williams - Half As Much - Bear Family CD (2005)


Like the first volume of Curley Williams' western swing music collection, volume two also covers his complete Columbia recordings, including all his early recordings from 1945-1952, as well as ultra-rare demos with Hank Williams on Time Has Proven I Was Wrong and No, Not Now.' Curley went on to work with Hank Williams and write one of his biggest hits, Half As Much, but here he proves convincingly that he's much more than a footnote to the Hank Williams story.
